aggregatecolumn.name: AggregateColumn
aggregatecolumn.description: Contains methods for describing summary fields such as Record Count, Sum, Average, Max, Min, and custom summary formulas. Includes name, label, data type, and grouping context.

bucketfield.name: BucketField
bucketfield.description: Contains methods and constructors to work with information about a bucket field, including bucket type, name, and bucketed values.

bucketfieldvalue.name: BucketFieldValue
bucketfieldvalue.description: Contains information about the report values included in a bucket field.

buckettype.name: BucketType
buckettype.description: The types of values included in a bucket.

columndatatype.name: ColumnDataType
columndatatype.description: The Reports.ColumnDataType enum describes the type of data in a column. It is returned by the getDataType method.

columnsortorder.name: ColumnSortOrder
columnsortorder.description: The Reports.ColumnSortOrder enum describes the order that the grouping column uses to sort data.

crossfilter.name: CrossFilter
crossfilter.description: Contains methods and constructors used to work with information about a cross filter.

csfgrouptype.name: CsfGroupType
csfgrouptype.description: The group level at which the custom summary format aggregate is displayed in a report.

dategranularity.name: DateGranularity
dategranularity.description: The Reports.DateGranularity enum describes the date interval that is used for grouping.

detailcolumn.name: DetailColumn
detailcolumn.description: Contains methods for describing fields that contain detailed data. Detailed data fields are also listed in the report metadata.

dimension.name: Dimension
dimension.description: Contains information for each row or column grouping.

evaluatedcondition.name: EvaluatedCondition
evaluatedcondition.description: Contains the individual components of an evaluated condition for a report notification, such as the aggregate name and label, the operator, and the value that the aggregate is compared to.

evaluatedconditionoperator.name: EvaluatedConditionOperator
evaluatedconditionoperator.description: The Reports.EvaluatedConditionOperator enum describes the type of operator used to compare an aggregate to a value. It is returned by the getOperator method.

filteroperator.name: FilterOperator
filteroperator.description: Contains information about a filter operator, such as display name and API name.

filtervalue.name: FilterValue
filtervalue.description: Contains information about a filter value, such as the display name and API name.

formulatype.name: FormulaType
formulatype.description: The format of the numbers in a custom summary formula.

groupingcolumn.name: GroupingColumn
groupingcolumn.description: Contains methods for describing fields that are used for column grouping.

groupinginfo.name: GroupingInfo
groupinginfo.description: Contains methods for describing fields that are used for grouping.

groupingvalue.name: GroupingValue
groupingvalue.description: Contains grouping values for a row or column, including the key, label, and value.

notificationaction.name: NotificationAction
notificationaction.description: Implement this interface to trigger a custom Apex class when the conditions for a report notification are met.

notificationactioncontext.name: NotificationActionContext
notificationactioncontext.description: Contains information about the report instance and condition threshold for a report notification.

reportcsf.name: ReportCsf
reportcsf.description: Contains methods and constructors for working with information about a custom summary formula (CSF).

reportcurrency.name: ReportCurrency
reportcurrency.description: Contains information about a currency value, including the amount and currency code.

reportdatacell.name: ReportDataCell
reportdatacell.description: Contains the data for a cell in the report, including the display label and value.

reportdescriberesult.name: ReportDescribeResult
reportdescriberesult.description: Contains report, report type, and extended metadata for a tabular, summary, or matrix report.

reportdetailrow.name: ReportDetailRow
reportdetailrow.description: Contains data cells for a detail row of a report.

reportdivisioninfo.name: ReportDivisionInfo
reportdivisioninfo.description: Contains information about the divisions that can be used to filter a report.

reportextendedmetadata.name: ReportExtendedMetadata
reportextendedmetadata.description: Contains report extended metadata for a tabular, summary, or matrix report.

reportfact.name: ReportFact
reportfact.description: Contains the fact map for the report, which represents the report’s data values.

reportfactwithdetails.name: ReportFactWithDetails
reportfactwithdetails.description: Contains the detailed fact map for the report, which represents the report’s data values.

reportfactwithsummaries.name: ReportFactWithSummaries
reportfactwithsummaries.description: Contains the fact map for the report, which represents the report’s data values, and includes summarized fields.

reportfilter.name: ReportFilter
reportfilter.description: Contains information about a report filter, including column, operator, and value.

reportformat.name: ReportFormat
reportformat.description: Contains the possible report format types.

reportinstance.name: ReportInstance
reportinstance.description: Returns an instance of a report that was run asynchronously. Retrieves the results for that instance.

reportmanager.name: ReportManager
reportmanager.description: Runs a report synchronously or asynchronously and with or without details.

reportmetadata.name: ReportMetadata
reportmetadata.description: Contains report metadata for a tabular, summary, or matrix report.

reportresults.name: ReportResults
reportresults.description: Contains the results of running a report.

reportscopeinfo.name: ReportScopeInfo
reportscopeinfo.description: Contains information about possible scope values that you can choose. Scope values depend on the report type. For example, you can set the scope for opportunity reports to All opportunities, My team’s opportunities, or My opportunities.

reportscopevalue.name: ReportScopeValue
reportscopevalue.description: Contains information about a possible scope value. Scope values depend on the report type. For example, you can set the scope for opportunity reports to All opportunities, My team’s opportunities, or My opportunities.

reporttype.name: ReportType
reporttype.description: Contains the unique API name and display name for the report type.

reporttypecolumn.name: ReportTypeColumn
reporttypecolumn.description: Contains detailed report type metadata about a field, including data type, display name, and filter values.

reporttypecolumncategory.name: ReportTypeColumnCategory
reporttypecolumncategory.description: Information about categories of fields in a report type.

reporttypemetadata.name: ReportTypeMetadata
reporttypemetadata.description: Contains report type metadata, which gives you information about the fields that are available in each section of the report type, plus filter information for those fields.

sortcolumn.name: SortColumn
sortcolumn.description: Contains information about the sort column used in the report.

standarddatefilter.name: StandardDateFilter
standarddatefilter.description: Contains information about standard date filter available in the report—for example, the API name, start date, and end date of the standard date filter duration as well as the API name of the date field on which the filter is placed.

standarddatefilterduration.name: StandardDateFilterDuration
standarddatefilterduration.description: Contains information about each standard date filter—also referred to as a relative date filter. It contains the API name and display label of the standard date filter duration as well as the start and end dates.

standarddatefilterdurationgroup.name: StandardDateFilterDurationGroup
standarddatefilterdurationgroup.description: Contains information about the standard date filter groupings, such as the grouping display label and all standard date filters that fall under the grouping. Groupings include Calendar Year, Calendar Quarter, Calendar Month, Calendar Week, Fiscal Year, Fiscal Quarter, Day, and custom values based on user-defined date ranges.

standardfilter.name: StandardFilter
standardfilter.description: Contains information about the standard filter defined in the report, such as the filter field API name and filter value.

standardfilterinfo.name: StandardFilterInfo
standardfilterinfo.description: Is an abstract base class for an object that provides standard filter information.

standardfilterinfopicklist.name: StandardFilterInfoPicklist
standardfilterinfopicklist.description: Contains information about the standard filter picklist, such as the display name and type of the filter field, the default picklist value, and a list of all possible picklist values.

standardfiltertype.name: StandardFilterType
standardfiltertype.description: The StandardFilterType enum describes the type of standard filters in a report. The getType() method returns a Reports.StandardFilterType enum value.

summaryvalue.name: SummaryValue
summaryvalue.description: Contains summary data for a cell of the report.

thresholdinformation.name: ThresholdInformation
thresholdinformation.description: Contains a list of evaluated conditions for a report notification.

toprows.name: TopRows
toprows.description: Contains methods and constructors for working with information about a row limit filter.
